// Brand-aware LangChain zero-to-hero diagram: langchain-ecosystem-map
direction: right

lc: LangChain { icon: ../icons/langchain/langchain.svg }
py: Python { icon: ../icons/langchain/python.svg }
pg: Postgres { icon: ../icons/langchain/postgresql.svg }
